            <p style="margin-left: 10%; margin-right: 10%; font-size: 18px; color: grey;">Out are the days of not knowing exactly what you are inviting to your group. LFG through Destinder automatically brings in the most relevant stats for whatever gametpe they are posting for.</p>
            <p style="margin-left: 10%; margin-right: 10%; font-size: 18px; color: grey;">Wnat someone with a specific ELO ranking? You can filter for that. Want to find people who have beaten the raid more than 1 time? Yeah easy to see that as well. Our advanced statistical tracking and filtering system allows you to find exactly
