            <p style="margin-left: 10%; margin-right: 10%; font-size: 18px; color: grey;">Ever run with another really good player that you wish your new potential fireteam member could easily see as well? With LFG through Destinder, it's incredibly easy to tag a another player for others to see who you are playing with, along
