            <p style="margin-left: 10%; margin-right: 10%; font-size: 18px; color: grey;">Gone are the days of not knowing what the other fireteam members skill level is when you join a <strong>Trials of Osiris Group</strong>. Gone are the days of people joining, just to rage quit. Destinder LFG allows full transparency before
